I Love You, Man;;74;;83;;R;;As his wedding day approaches, Peter Klaven (Paul Rudd) realizes he has no one to act as his best man. Through a series of "man-dates," he finds Sydney Fife (Jason Segel), and the pair become instant friends. But as Peter's "bro-mance" with Sydney grows stronger, it threatens his relationship with his fiancee (Rashida Jones), forcing Peter to make a choice.;;Comedy;;John Hamburg;;2009;;Paul Rudd,Jason Segel,Rashida Jones,Jaime Pressly,Andy Samberg,J.K. Simmons,Jane Curtin,Jon Favreau,Sarah Burns,Rob Huebel,Joe Lo Truglio,Lou Ferrigno,Thomas Lennon;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/i_love_you_man